<section class="section" data-section-id="{{ section.id }}">
  <div class="card" style="max-width:800px;margin:0 auto">
    <h2 style="color:var(--color-text);margin-bottom:20px;font-size:28px;font-weight:700">Why We Started</h2>
    <p style="color:var(--color-text-light);line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:16px">We saw American homeowners struggling to find the right outdoor surface material. Concrete looks plain. Loose gravel shifts. Pavers crack. We believe there's a better way — bonded stone surfaces that look natural, stay in place, and transform ordinary outdoor spaces into beautiful living areas.</p>
    <p style="color:var(--color-text-light);line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:16px">TerraBond Outdoor was built to serve two audiences: the DIY homeowner who wants to upgrade their backyard, and the professional contractor who needs reliable, beautiful materials for client projects.</p>
    <p style="color:var(--color-text-light);line-height:1.8">Our sample-first approach means you never have to guess about color. See the real stone in your own light, on your own patio, before planning a bulk material order.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <h2 class="section-title">Our Approach</h2>
  <div class="card-grid" style="max-width:900px;margin:0 auto">
    <div class="card text-center"><div class="card-icon" style="margin:0 auto 20px"><i data-lucide="palette" style="width:28px;height:28px"></i></div><h3>Sample First</h3><p>Order real cured samples before committing to bulk materials.</p></div>
    <div class="card text-center"><div class="card-icon" style="margin:0 auto 20px"><i data-lucide="clipboard-list" style="width:28px;height:28px"></i></div><h3>Project Guidance</h3><p>Every project estimate gets a human review, not an automated quote.</p></div>
    <div class="card text-center"><div class="card-icon" style="margin:0 auto 20px"><i data-lucide="handshake" style="width:28px;height:28px"></i></div><h3>Dealer Partnership</h3><p>We support contractors and dealers with wholesale pricing and project support.</p></div>
  </div>
</section>

